Description: InstantLocal delivers unforgettable authentic local experiences using AI to personalize options for every traveler.
Full Description: InstantLocal is a social platform for travelers and the travel sector. Targeted at digitally savvy travelers InstantLocal is enhancing urban travel with cognitive AI and machine learning. InstantLocal learns a traveler’s interests and behaviors to provide tailored local experience options. Using AI and machine learning, InstantLocal delivers personalized local experience options including business services, tours, events, entertainment, wellness opportunities, local attractions and posts from other travelers. The business will provide opportunity for location based promotions and for subscriptions to data insights. Vance Reavie, Robert Turner and Gabriel Killian are experienced entrepreneurs specializing in web and in internet based technologies, data engineering, digital marketing and consulting. The founders have grown and successfully exited several businesses. InstantLocal beta-launched on the web, Apple and Google app stores in January-August 2017. The beta period included Austin and Dallas/Fort Worth, TX featuring 800+ business, and 500+ app users. With input from 100’s of engagements and testing sessions with locals, local businesses and peak industry associations InstantLocal is addresses key challenges and opportunities in the travel and hospitality sectors. The new AI-enhanced app is rolling out in 20 US cities in Q4 2017/Q1 2018.

Organization Name: Ehline Law Firm Personal Injury Attorneys APLC
Description: A personal injury law firm focusing on assisting downtrodden victims of catastrophic accidents and death claims.
Headquarters Regions: Greater Los Angeles Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Michael Ehline, the president of  Ehline Law Firm Personal Injury Attorneys APLC, is an honorably discharged United States Marine who went on to become a lawyer on the California State Bar Law Office Study Program with no undergrad.  His friend, attorney Gary Dordick, helped him gain admission into the University of West Los Angeles School of Law, where he attended classes at night to earn his Juris Doctorate, after he was already a practicing, duly admitted attorney. Prior to this, Ehline worked as a paralegal for several of the most prominent catastrophic injury lawyers in Greater Los Angeles. Ehline is admitted to practice law California Supreme Court and several federal courts, and tried three cases to the jury while he was still in law school, as a Certified Law Student.  In the last 10 years, Michael Ehline has recovered more than $30,000,000.00 for seriously injured victims who had suffered injuries due to no fault of their own. Mr. Ehline focuses on vehicular accidents, with spine and lumbar injuries being primary area of his law practice.  He is a prolific author and motorcycle rider, and is known in the injured biker community as the: "Motorcycle Rider's Friend."  Los Angeles Magazine has named Mr. Ehline Southern California SuperLawyer's Rising Star in the last 5 years in a row from 2009 - 2014. Only about 5% of lawyers are chosen to be Rising Stars, based upon being secretly chosen by their peers, based upon having achieved recognition above and beyond a typical, average attorney. Ehline is also a member of the Million Dollar Advocates Forum, which is also known for being one of the top litigation lawyer organizations in the US. In fact, this organization is so elite, because so few lawyers have ever achieved that million dollar plus verdict or settlement.  Ehline was also selected by the Circle of Legal Trust as one of the most trustworthy and prolific attorneys online from 2012 - 2014. The highly prestigious Circle of Legal Trust is an invitation only organization and requires a vote of original board members to be considered for membership. Michael Ehline also serves as a member of multitude of professional organizations, inter alia, including the American Judicature Society (AJS), Consumer Attorneys of Los Angeles (CAALA), Consumer Attorneys Of California (CAOC), the South Bay Bar Association (SBBA), American Inns of Court, Web of Trust, and Marine Corps. Association (MCA.) Additionally, Ehline is a member of the International Motorcycle Lawyer Association (IMLA), International Society of Truck Injury Lawyers (ISTIL), and the Bus and Carriage Injury Attorney's Association (BCIAA). Mr. Ehline has led numerous legal organizations, and acted as a guest speaker at Southwestern Law School on behalf of retired Appellate Justice J. Gary Hastings, and has also spoken on behalf of the American Paralegals association. In addition, Ehline has lobbied congress in Washington DC on behalf of the International Cruise Victims Association (ICV.)  Mr. Ehline is a member of Spinal Cord Meeting, which is an international association of attorneys and doctors worldwide, who discuss the latest technology and treatment for back and related spine injuries. Ehline is also a member of the National Spinal Cord Injury Association, the Brain Injury Association of California, and the North American Brain Injury Society, to name just a few. Ehline is a frequent Google HOA speaker for Circle of Legal Trust, and also heavily involved in training and teaching prospective law students for Law Office Study Net, a group dedicated to teaching less fortunate individuals how to become attorneys by reading for the law. Ehline himself has participated as an extra in films, including a music video by musician, Rylee Preston, dedicated to helping returning war veterans. Ehline has also been a guest on the Nancy Grace Show, and has been featured in California Lawyer Magazine, the Daily Journal, CNN and Noticias. Ehline is dedicated to assisting downtrodden individuals as their legal champion.

Description: Battery Medics, LLC was created to help hard working people and companies, save money on battery replacement costs.
Full Description: Battery Medics, LLC was created to help hard working people and companies, save money on battery replacement costs. With high rising battery prices in everyday vehicles, electric forklifts, RV`s, golf carts, etc., Instead of replacing batteries in these daily vehicles, they can prolong the life of the battery by 3-5 years more and save customers long  costs of each time a battery needs replaced and put that money back into your pocket. The product and procedures they use are top notch and the product is a tried and proven product by over 25+yrs by a strict company that I have contracted with to provide us with the battery chemicals to use for this service. Being an auto mechanic for over 15 yrs, I`ve decided to become an entrepreneur and life a healthy and debt free lifestyle for myself and family. Over the years, i was told that to open up my own garage and become free from the rat race. I`ve researched it many times over and seen the high costs and stress it will take to run my own garage. Rent, insurance, fees, taxes, equipment, etc., were out of my budget back then and now. But, after doing research on this product the last 2 years and alot of phone time and trying the product myself and on friends and family vehicles, it works no problem. But not with just the product, comes with procedures of testing the battery before and after, cleaning the battery, load testing, letting batteries sit for "wait time" and such. But, as of researching banks for loans and such, i`ve noticed that banks pretty much tell start up businesses NO without good credit and at least a year in business.. I have neither.. But am willing to work for what i want to get this going and do the research to get a "hand" in helping obtain a business vehicle and some business equipment to get the ball rolling and hit the ground running. But with 2 little girls and bills, its hard to save money to do what I need to do. SO i come to this site for potential investors to help me out and get going.
